 Hành chính - Thư ký','304 Trịnh Thị Miếng, Ấp Đông, thới Tam thôn, Hóc Môn, HCM','2','1 năm','Chuyên viên- nhân viên','14 - 20 triệu','Cao đẳng','1. Daily • Import custom clearance (CDS): + Collecting (invoice, packing list/details PL,BL, CO,…) from person in charges or suppliers and correcting docs if any + Creating code of materials + Checking HS code for new items + Using Ecuss to transfer CDS and scan final docs to attach Ecuss + Recording Original docs • C/O + Form C/O: VK, AANZ, D… + Making material detail list to submit MOIT or VCCI + Following balanced materials + Collecting domestic red invoice and import CDS to make CO • Processing contract: + Creating Code for materials and products + Opening processing contract per year and liquidation + Following sub-processing contracts + Following and balancing BOM (Định Mức) + Following approval for processing contract factory infrastructure 2. Report: • Doing liquidation processing contract report • Balance materials by BOM in Ecus • Year-end balance report (Báo cáo quyết toán) • Weekly Ecus material balance by BOM to all parties and Korean managers 3. Other: • Tasks will be assigned by Korean managers • Checking costs related to shipment if incurred to managers • Supporting accounting if any related docs.','- Graduated from College related to import-export or foreign trade. - Have at least 1 years of experience in the field of import and export.','06/07/2024','{\'description\': \'Công Ty TNHH Đông Nam Việt Nam (Dong Nam Co., Ltd)06/07/2024\', \'src\': \'https://cdn1.vieclam24h.vn/images/old_employer_avatar/images/a85fd3de1a1c4c62a31f63094ff979f0_1527648004_ng_nam.png\'}','https://vieclam24h.vn/det-may-da-giay-thoi-trang/exim-staff-for-processing-garment-company-c40p122id200360454.html','vieclam24h',NULL,'2024-06-06 09:18:52','2024-06-06 09:18:52',49,NULL,NULL,0),(1353,'Nhân Viên Kế Toán','1717520400000','Bình Định , Phú Yên','None','None','None','Toàn thời gian cố định','- Lương từ 4.5tr – 10tr thỏa thuận theo năn